data.description: Move in ready just in time for the holidays! This house features a open floor plan with three bedrooms and two bathrooms. Very well maintained home on cul de sac and walking distance from revitalized downtown Fate and parks. Property has the largest lot in Spring Meadow at almost a half an acre. Interior of home features open concept floor plan, luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, stainless steel appliances (2019), bathroom vanities (2019), surround sound, security alarm and cameras, flat screen tv in living room, walk in closets in all bedrooms. Huge fenced backyard with dog run, covered wood deck with fans for hot summer nights and flat screen mount with plug ins for all the football games. This lot and location is perfect for entertainment and any future back yard plans. You also have no backyard neighbors!!
